le=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 22, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104pqq1665702712261_2.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pqq1665702712261_2.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pqq1665702712261_2.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"pqq1665702712261\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Alignment\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specify how the data is aligned in the field.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pqq1665702712261__section_w2101ab1b5b1_w2102ab1b5_w2103ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"pqq1665702712261__table_d11246e1_d11247e1_d11248e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"pqq1665702712261__table_d11246e1_d11247e1_d11248e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"pqq1665702712261__table_d11246e1_d11247e1_d11248e1__entry__2\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pqq1665702712261__table_d11246e1_d11247e1_d11248e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">(default)</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pqq1665702712261__table_d11246e1_d11247e1_d11248e1__entry__2\">Use system defaults. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pqq1665702712261__table_d11246e1_d11247e1_d11248e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Left</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pqq1665702712261__table_d11246e1_d11247e1_d11248e1__entry__2\">\n Data is left-aligned. This is the default for all fields except boilerplate fields.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pqq1665702712261__table_d11246e1_d11247e1_d11248e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Right</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pqq1665702712261__table_d11246e1_d11247e1_d11248e1__entry__2\">\n Uniface aligns the data from the right.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pqq1665702712261__table_d11246e1_d11247e1_d11248e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Centered</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pqq1665702712261__table_d11246e1_d11247e1_d11248e1__entry__2\">Data is centered in the field. This is the\n                        default for boilerplate fields. <p class=\"p\">When used in an edit box, if the text is\n                           longer than the field width, the text is not scrolled to show the text in\n                           the center of the field.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pqq1665702712261__table_d11246e1_d11247e1_d11248e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Decimal</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pqq1665702712261__table_d11246e1_d11247e1_d11248e1__entry__2\">\n Data is aligned to the decimal point or comma, as defined in the display format.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pqq1665702712261__section_w12_1f3_pwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d927014e157\">Description</h2>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"pqq1665702712261__note_yw2_bf3_pwb\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> Due to limitations in the underlying Windows\n            controls, it is not possible to right align or center edit box or multiline edit box\n            fields that are too small to display the data and that have the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Automatic\n               Word Wrap</span> or <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Transparency</span> properties\n            selected.</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pqq1665702712261__section_qsj_bf3_pwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d927014e172\">Applies to</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"pqq1665702712261__ul_icz_cf3_pwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"pqq1665702712261__li_d3755e1_d3756e1_d3757e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ijx1665702711766.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ijx1665702711766.html\" title=\"A Modeled Field Layout is a Development Object that defines the way data is displayed.\">Modeled Field Layout</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cwt1665702639216.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Automatic Word Wrap</a><p>Determines whether text is automatically wrapped to the next line when it exceeds the width of the widget. This also disables the horizontal scroll bar, if defined. True or False (default).</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kvj1665702609788.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Transparency</a><p>Determines whether the widget is transparent.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8421808\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8421808\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Alignment Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 22, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Alignment Specify how the data is aligned in the field. Value Description (default) Use system defaults. Left Data is left-aligned. This is the default for all fields except boilerplate fields. Right Uniface aligns the data from the right. Centered Data is centered in the field. This is the default for boilerplate fields. When used in an edit box, if the text is longer than the field width, the text is not scrolled to show the text in the center of the field. Decimal Data is aligned to the decimal point or comma, as defined in the display format. Description Note: Due to limitations in the underlying Windows controls, it is not possible to right align or center edit box or multiline edit box fields that are too small to display the data and that have the Automatic Word Wrap or Transparency properties selected. Applies to Modeled Field Layout Related Links Automatic Word Wrap Determines whether text is automatically wrapped to the next line when it exceeds the width of the widget. This also disables the horizontal scroll bar, if defined. True or False (default). Transparency Determines whether the widget is transparent. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}